What is it?
===========
My personal Boilerplate with some cool tools:
- Composer: to get some PHP packages on http://packagist.org/
- Silex: nice PHP microframework http://silex.sensiolabs.org/
- Twig: modern template engine for PHP http://twig.sensiolabs.org/
- Initializr: HTML5 templates generator based on HTML5 boilerplate http://www.initializr.com/
- Bootstrap Twitter 2: http://twitter.github.com/bootstrap/


How to use
==========
- Clone these sources
- get needed PHP packages with composer
- customize your template (under views and views/pages)


Install packages with composer
==============================
Install composer:
$ curl -s http://getcomposer.org/installer | php

Install packages with composer:
$ php composer.phar install

